{"tid":1456610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遍地開花以眼還眼！","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:54.000Z","uid":74028,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a44fa5ebecbe24897048039b03dc8f5d87b47ee2","tid":1456610,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"利伸絕無散水之意，以下全為發夢夢景<br />\n<br />\n純綷想商量下，未入機場但想入既人唔一定係得機場而個選擇，例如狗屋等等<br />\n<br />\n第一 今日既目的係以眼還眼，利用機場去俾其他人知道香港發生緊既事，但機場停哂機，遊客又少甚至無既情況下，係做唔到一開頭接機做文宣既效果，而癱瘓機場而個目的亦都係唔成立，因為已經停左，你仲想癱瘓啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n第二 機場封鎖哂只會變成戰場，用催淚彈橡膠子彈高走唔甩咖啦，繼而係各種圍捕，即使一個定一百個都唔係我地想見到既野。<br />\n<br />\n第三 機場咁重狗力既時候，其他位會唔會係一個好啲既開花地方？"},{"pid":"01605afaba500eacf6ebf47bf3916fd4583122cb","tid":1456610,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"257a533620de313da9c561d2aa454ba178ef02d4","tid":1456610,"uid":225347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"唔止眼，仲有以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10f8baf920880d3d42d7a319accf061e07dac1b","tid":1456610,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"257a533620de313da9c561d2aa454ba178ef02d4","tid":1456610,"uid":225347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"唔止眼，仲有以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"搞其他位有無可行之處？"},{"pid":"3b26de7076cfe33137762c890da791b64addb866","tid":1456610,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9d9b4b0ccf6ef6100d1a279db448295d8246f9c5","tid":1456610,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"731e8ca74ad71bc3bdf6c697f93dcb405997b998","tid":1456610,"uid":284571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:41:52.0