":"2019-08-13T01:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c6de575c4752df5b0f68c06206789c89cb6bc0","tid":1456610,"uid":295226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:54.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;&lt;轉自中環私家醫生：&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">警察記招提及有警察在示威中有二級燒傷，藉此緩減警察打爆女仔眼睛的責任。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">甚麽是二級燒傷呢？</span></strong><br />\n原來<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">起水泡已經係二級燒傷</span></span></strong>，皮膚局部燒傷，依然在有痛楚感覺咁解。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">二级燒傷的嚴重程度在於位置，如果燒親眼睛就係嚴重受傷。 如果是小腿燒傷，通常都係可以敷藥後痊癒。</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">與打爆眼及有永久傷殘不能相提並論！</span></span></span></strong>"}]}